    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏎 Early Access Disclaimer 🏎</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Circuit Racers is in active development. This Early Access version contains a portion of the planned content, with new features, tracks, and improvements arriving regularly. By joining now, you’ll help shape the future of the game through your feedback and suggestions. Expect frequent updates, balance tweaks, and additional modes as we work toward the full release.</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077970/extras/c695ddf0ceac43b0e31b3768da132ac3.poster.avif?t=1754791309\" width=400 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077970/extras/c695ddf0ceac43b0e31b3768da132ac3.webm?t=1754791309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Race through the leader board with your skills, beat the track and your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077970/extras/ecdd0656e6e8485aa4cafbf752593f68.poster.avif?t=1754791309\" width=500 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077970/extras/ecdd0656e6e8485aa4cafbf752593f68.webm?t=1754791309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single player</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller Support</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Changeable Background Music</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this go kart racer you are in an open world with multiple tracks to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go to the pits and choose your GO-KARTS and customize your Racer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077970/extras/ed8d2507bbf90cd6ce5d4738612b8af7.poster.avif?t=1754791309\" width=500 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077970/extras/ed8d2507bbf90cd6ce5d4738612b8af7.webm?t=1754791309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable GO - KARTS</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Player</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>(The description of this game is not finished and will be updated to represent the features in game)</strong></i></u></p>",
